quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaa…ďe e mun, wanaa baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe woodani, mawnii konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wowlaali si wanaa fenaande"
  18,6,"Bala jo'o an a tanpinay hoore-maa e dow batteeji ma…ď…ďe, si gom…óinaali ndee Yewtere ka suno"
  18,7,"Menen Men wa…óii ko woni kon ka hoore leydi cu…óaari mayri, fii yo Men jarribo …ďe ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďurata mo∆ī∆īinnde golle"
  18,8,Menen ko Men wa…óoo…ďe ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yim…ďe fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi …óin, …óun wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaa…ďe …ďen sorunoo ka fammeere, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka Maa…óa Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin ka nder fammeere limoore duu…ďi
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini …ďe fii yo Men fen√Īinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle …óen …ói…ói …ďuri moftude [limoore] ko …ďe √Īii…ďi kon dummunne"
  18,13,"Menen Me…óen fillanaade ma kumpital fii ma…ď…ďe e Goonga, …ďen …óon, ko sukaa…ďe gom…óin…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe Men …ďeydani …ďe Peewal"
  18,14,"Men ha…ď…ďi e dow …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tuma nde …ďe darinoo, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko Jey…óo On kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo rewetee…óo, gom…óii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"∆Āee yim…ďe amen, …ďe jogitike ko woori Mo rewetee…ói, ko haaanunoo ko yo …ďe addu e dow ma…ď…ďe dalil …ďanngu…óo. Ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īude ko foti e on fefindii…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla"
